{"tid":2326730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【好人好事】深水埗髮型屋推「失業免費」服務！網民大讚人間有愛","createTime":"2020-12-15T13:42:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T13:44:31.000Z","uid":271829,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"74107311ec4819cb2f6ca00d2de22b3f7f8d9f80","tid":2326730,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T13:42:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2825000/2829234/ssp0_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2825000%2F2829234%2Fssp0_1024.jpg&h=5605015d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情已持續一年，不少企業都終於捱不住，而不少人更在聖誕節前失去工作。有良心小店近日就決定推出「失業免費」服務，助有需要人士捱過難關！<br />\n<br />\n深水埗髮型屋「The One Cut 一剪」近日在官方 Facebook 出帖，表示雖然舖頭受到經濟環境影響，但仍有能力幫有需要的人。所以，決定一連 7 天推出免費單剪服務，失業或有困難的人士只要在 7-9pm 時段內告知師傅情況，就可享用免費服務。官方亦在帖文中暖心表示：「大家要加油，一定會捱得過架！」<br />\n<br />\n不少網民見到後都留下抱抱或心心 emoji，又留言指出：「抵囋！」、「人間有愛」、「感謝香港人互相解困！」、「好人好事」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2825000/2829234/ssp1_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2825000%2F2829234%2Fssp1_600.jpg&h=019cf372&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n良心髮型屋近日推出「失業免費」服務，一連 7 天  7-9pm 時段，向失業或有困難人士提供免費服務。"},{"pid":"72ca3f067e953331513b423d82c731f1b7e879cb","tid":2326730,"uid":127579,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T13:43:18.000Z","msg":"免費打J?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9728ec30e9bf75ad57a0beda4fd1adf535931d0","tid":2326730,"uid":7452,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"72ca3f067e953331513b423d82c731f1b7e879cb","tid":2326730,"uid":127579,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T13:43:18.000Z","msg":"免費打J?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-1